Decentralized Knowledge Marketplace L1
Overview

Decentralized Knowledge Marketplace L1 enables users to share, sell, and access knowledge in a decentralized environment.

Features
Knowledge tokenization
Pay-per-access content
Contributor rewards
Reputation systems
Transparent transactions
Architecture
Knowledge Registry

Stores content metadata.

Access Control Layer

Manages permissions.

Payment Engine

Handles transactions.

Reputation System

Tracks contributor credibility.

Use Cases
Online education
Expert marketplaces
Research sharing
Knowledge platforms
